Bill, the amount of primary schools in special measures etc.</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">Since 6/9 I</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">visited the Head numerous times concerned that the school may be pursuing academy status.</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> I was consistently adv</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">ised to go through the Chair of Governors but this proved difficult as she appeared to be too busy to get in touch. Eventually she did ring</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">-</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> she told me that if there was a fight to be had she would have it, that she had lived in the area years and cared </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">much about the school.</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#222222; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> She went on at length about the reasons the previous Head had left wanting to pursue his career etc.</span><span style="background-